Enter Input : simply because he forgot him. While he was wearying every one with his
Enter Input : tears and complaints, and turning his house into a sink of debauchery, a
Enter Input : faithful servant of the family, Grigory, took the three-year-old Mitya
Enter Input : into his care. If he hadn’t looked after him there would have been no one
Enter Input : even to change the baby’s little shirt.
