Enter Input : daughters were married, so that Mitya remained for almost a whole year in
Enter Input : old Grigory’s charge and lived with him in the servant’s cottage. But if
Enter Input : his father had remembered him (he could not, indeed, have been altogether
Enter Input : unaware of his existence) he would have sent him back to the cottage, as
Enter Input : the child would only have been in the way of his debaucheries. But a
Enter Input : cousin of Mitya’s mother, Pyotr Alexandrovitch Miüsov, happened to return
