Enter Input : our bone, but one who has suffered and has seen so much more deeply than
Enter Input : we have his insight impresses us as wisdom... that wisdom of the heart
Enter Input : which we seek that we may learn from it how to live. All his other
Enter Input : gifts came to him from nature, this he won for himself and through it he
Enter Input : became great."
