Enter Input : before yesterday."
Enter Input : 
Enter Input : "I will bring you the interest for another month; wait a little."
Enter Input : 
Enter Input : "But that's for me to do as I please, my good sir, to wait or to sell
Enter Input : your pledge at once."
Enter Input : 
Enter Input : "How much will you give me for the watch, Alyona Ivanovna?"
Enter Input : 
